      <abstract>
	      <para>
		  	Libtododb is a API library to task information used by gpe-todo.
	      </para>
	  </abstract>
    <para>
	   Libtododb offers an API to access ToDo task data like used in gpe-todo.
	   It is used by gpe-todo itself and should be used from all applications
	   to read or modify ToDo data.
    </para>
